---
title: Pulled Duck Tacos with Chipotle Tomato Salsa and Sweet Potato Fries
description: Our warm taco tortillas are piled high with tender duck confit and served in the traditional way with fresh tomato salsa. The flavours in this dish are balanced out brilliantly with pickled onions, fresh herbs, and a chipotle mayo dressing that takes this recipe to new taste highs! A great thing to make for your next ‘Taco Tuesday’ or to share with friends over the weekend, this recipe will bring the warm Mexican sunshine straight to your kitchen.
